snippet.textDisplay:
This is the first time that I've loved all the songs from a season. Zulfiqar Jabbar Khan (Xulfi) has taken Coke Studio to the next level. I truly appreciate the entire team for their hard work and dedication. Thank you for giving us such beautiful music. These past few months have been some of the best in my life, and Coke Studio has become a part of my daily routine. Every song was better than the last, especially the final one. I feel quite sad that the season has come to an end. 
Once again, I appreciate the entire team and will eagerly await the next season. Until then, I'll keep enjoying these songs. Thank you once again for making such an amazing season.❤
